    "author_channel_id": "UC_JkoKaPmsWB94tq600xBug",
    "text": "One alternative for people who can't to go back to pre 5.2 Cura versions is to edit the model in Blender or similar modeling software and apply the modifier which turns it into a thick wireframe. It increases the triangle count significantly and doesn't take into account overhang limitations so it's not ideal but for the most part it should be usable.",
